run on Harvard Cannon compute cluster using the following athena++ setup:
https://github.com/morganemacleod/athena/blob/master/src/pgen/planet_wind_lambda_star_origin.cpp

Configuration command:
python configure.py --prob planet_wind_lambda_star_origin --coord spherical_polar -mpi -hdf5 --hdf5_path $HDF5_HOME --nscalars=2 --mpiccmd mpicxx --cflag " -xCORE-AVX512"

(note: requires the https://github.com/morganemacleod/athena athena fork) 
